# Filament Plugin Creator

## When to use

- Creating a new Filament plugin from scratch
- Managing Filament plugin branch strategy (1.x, 2.x, 3.x)
- Setting up plugin project structure (ServiceProvider, Resources, etc.)
- Publishing a Filament plugin to Packagist
- Upgrading a plugin across Filament versions (v3, v4, v5)

## Keywords

`filament plugin`, `filament package`, `plugin creation`, `1.x 2.x 3.x branches`, `filament service provider`, `plugin skeleton`
